1. Convert the data sets to .vcf.gz format.
plink2 --pfile data1 --export vcf bgz vcf-dosage=DS-force --out data1

2. index gz files /ludc/Tools/Software/bcftools/1.18/bin/bcftools --index BMI_snp_chr9.vcf.gz

3. Merge the .vcf.gz files using bcftools

3.1 list vcf
  ls *.vcf>list_vcf
3.2 sort

3.3 merge
/ludc/Tools/Software/bcftools/1.18/bin/bcftools concat  -f list_vcf_sorted -o BMI_snp_allchr
